             Leadership, I think we need A designated SGA leader (no I'm not nominating myself for this) that does not have power over the individual guilds per say but does set direction. This could be rotated out like terms of office.<br>
             Regular Raids, we need to set up more regular raids for all level ranges to get our members used to working together. The difference between us and larger guilds are that they do regular raids. They are used to working together on a regular basis. This also promotes keeping the members of our guilds from leaving.<br>
<br>
<br>
