Screaming Fist</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#6A74B4><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usarindal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sarindal</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>3/26/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>1:48:28 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fsaryrnguildallianceboardfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=114.topic&index=1><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Suggestion Box</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Well, concidering the situation, and how young the SGA really is, I think we've done a remarkable job simply getting  things to the point they're currently at. That said, it's probably wise to start shaping some things up right now, and it sounds like you've got things on a good track Zen.<br>
